# CODEOWNERS
# This file controls who is automatically requested for review when a pull
# request modifies the matched paths.
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything (replace with your GitHub handle)
* @yourname

# Skill definition
/SKILL.md @yourname
/metadata.json @yourname
/_meta.json @yourname

# Core scripts (highest scrutiny)
/scripts/ @yourname
/scripts/lib/ @yourname

# Search-engine submodule (vendored)
/search-engine/ @yourname

# Tests (any contributor may review)
/tests/ @yourname
/search-engine/tests/ @yourname

# Documentation
/README.md @yourname
/USER_GUIDE.md @yourname
/FAQ.md @yourname
/CHANGELOG.md @yourname
/CONTRIBUTING.md @yourname
/references/ @yourname
/examples/ @yourname

# Security
/SECURITY.md @yourname
/.github/ @yourname
